upload MP3s, set a similarity threshold, and interactively detect and play audio segments matching a sample clip.

pip install flask pydub numpy scipy


project/
├── app.py                # Flask backend with logic
├── templates/
│   └── index.html        # Web interface
├── static/
│   ├── uploads/          # Stores uploaded files
│   └── segments/         # Stores matched audio clips
└── match_log.txt         # (Optional) match log


python app.py to run the project

http://127.0.0.1:5001/

outcome.png is a sample that Similarity Threshold (%):10% 

